{
  "stem": "18778.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 344.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that actually was the reason why after the Nuremberg laws stopped Jews from having-- practicing their professions, he was eventually reinstated, because he was already in that field before World War I.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe his-- he was accepted to the bar in 1911.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1938.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found in our papers a letter where he requests that he be permitted to represent at least Jews only until the end of 1938.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was denied.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- the order for him to-- to decease-- to cease practicing came right after Crystal Night, which was in November of '38.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother came-- was the youngest of three sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think she was the most beautiful of the three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was a trained coloratura soprano singer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she used to entertain in Jewish circles sometimes, singing and play the guitar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- her father did not permit her to study.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She wanted to study medicine or she wanted to study art.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he just wanted her to stay home, look pretty, and play the piano.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's what she did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She-- she enjoyed traveling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And basically, she had no particular career of any kind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She got married at-- I think in-- they got married in 1927, so she was 26 years old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she ran a big household.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was a wonderful wife to my father and a very caring mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was in times of crisis a Goliath.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then afterwards, she'd break down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were many times when her strength was called upon in her lifetime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, when I was six, I had a very difficult middle ear infection and a consequent operation, mastoid operation.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
